Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.67,0:00:07.09,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}爱恋是惊悚 冲击 悬疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.30,0:00:10.67,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}无形的力量 依靠着…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.80,0:00:18.27,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}请不要紧闭你的心扉 紧紧地…紧紧地…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.38,0:00:20.95,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}在坚定无比的内心里充满推理的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.10,0:00:22.92,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k172}永远以最坚强的节奏揭开案情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.96,0:00:24.85,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k187}今天事件和谎言一起解决
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.06,0:00:26.84,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}美丽委托人的真实身份出人意料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.11,0:00:28.52,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k205}唯一看透真相的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.68,0:00:30.37,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k157}外表看似小孩 头脑却是大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.47,0:00:32.61,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k179}他的名字就是 名侦探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.36,0:00:36.28,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k289}或许我也想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:36.85,0:00:46.94,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}让你感受到与我相同感受的刺痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.06,0:00:53.32,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是什么让自己心痛 是什么让自己畏惧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.45,0:00:57.91,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}纠葛不清的二人真实面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.04,0:01:01.46,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}害怕去面对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.33,0:01:06.89,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}爱恋是惊悚 冲击 悬疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:07.01,0:01:14.09,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}即使困惑随着清风飞逝 想永远躺在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.24,0:01:17.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你小小的胸膛里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.72,0:01:21.16,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}请不要紧闭你的心扉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.29,0:01:25.69,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}即使对于自己的未来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.81,0:01:35.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}有着新的迷惘与不安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.88,0:01:46.94,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}侦探事务所来了位漂亮的委托人池波静华女士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.14,0:01:56.15,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}委托的任务是寻找初中时代的同学 同剑道部的柴田四朗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.60,0:01:59.62,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}目标人物马上就找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.47,0:02:02.88,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k287}在静冈担任体育老师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.20,0:02:07.79,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我们立刻前往他的住处
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.16,0:02:10.37,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}到了那里发现的是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.65,0:02:13.84,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k248}已经被杀害的柴田四朗先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.39,0:02:19.57,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}手里握着三十年前的池波静华女士的照片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.48,0:02:24.17,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}身份不明满口谎言的委托人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.81,0:02:26.97,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}所说的几乎都是谎话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.24,0:02:31.75,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}到底 她隐瞒的是些什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.32,0:02:41.53,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}满口谎言的委托人（后篇）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.75,0:02:46.76,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}横沟警官 我们发现了一把沾满血迹疑似凶器的木刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.22,0:02:47.73,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}真的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.97,0:02:48.53,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k75}是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.83,0:02:53.13,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k185}发现的地点是在玄关旁边的逃生楼梯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.84,0:02:56.53,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}柴田太太 你们家有木刀吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.54,0:03:00.78,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}有 放在那个鞋柜上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.36,0:03:04.59,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我丈夫来用它赶走那些纠缠不休的推销员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.21,0:03:06.71,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}现在并没有看到啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.21,0:03:10.39,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k201}还有 你家共有几个电话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.19,0:03:13.71,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}客厅和卧室共两个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.86,0:03:17.18,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}本来玄关也有的 可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.33,0:03:21.31,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}原来如此 我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.82,0:03:25.83,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k250}犯人是池波女士 就是你对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.88,0:03:28.94,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}拜托…横沟警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.38,0:03:33.43,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k250}你事先打过电话 确认那张照片的位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.64,0:03:37.53,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}为了拿回那张照片 你今天早上已经来过这里了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.99,0:03:41.98,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}可是你们为了照片的事情在玄关发生争执
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.60,0:03:46.28,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}于是你一时冲动 就用鞋柜上的木刀砍了对方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.72,0:03:51.67,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你以为把四朗先生杀死了 就从逃生楼梯逃走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.14,0:03:56.83,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那时候柴田先生还没断气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.12,0:03:59.44,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}他在地板上拼命地爬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.89,0:04:01.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k177}想要爬到客厅打电话求救
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.29,0:04:03.62,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k240}可是他的身体却动不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.40,0:04:09.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这时映入他眼中的就是那本夹着你的照片的书
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.05,0:04:13.83,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}于是柴田先生用尽最后的力气 把书架前堆放的书推倒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.20,0:04:19.85,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}然后握着犯人的照片断气了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.71,0:04:22.87,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}可是 光凭一张照片…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.46,0:04:26.46,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k275}这张照片里大概有什么秘密吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.14,0:04:32.67,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}所以和毛利先生一起返回命案现场 目的就是取回照片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.42,0:04:38.31,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}池波女士 可以请你跟我们到警局走一趟吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.71,0:04:41.01,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我拒绝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.38,0:04:46.07,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}如果想要请我去接受讯问的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.19,0:04:50.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k280}就请你先去向法院申请拘捕令吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.87,0:04:56.04,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不过 让法院发布拘捕令需要的证据
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.10,0:04:58.25,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}以现阶段来看并不充分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.45,0:05:03.25,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k234}我想你是申请不到拘捕令强迫我去警察局的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.28,0:05:09.84,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}当然 如果柴田太太起诉我们五人非法入侵民宅的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.04,0:05:11.45,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那就另当别论了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.59,0:05:16.58,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}什么呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.81,0:05:19.96,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k222}这个女人 到底是什么人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.99,0:05:24.38,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你看他的左手都沾满了血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.81,0:05:26.84,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}大概是摸到头上的伤口吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.50,0:05:28.94,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k269}不过真奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.37,0:05:32.59,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k186}他手指上的绷带并没有沾到血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.69,0:05:35.81,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}对了 那个女人的左手也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.26,0:05:41.17,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}等一下 那他的右手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.10,0:05:42.92,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k284}喂 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.80,0:05:50.44,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}原来如此 是这么回事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.80,0:05:53.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不行啊 真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.95,0:05:56.36,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}犯人果然是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.21,0:05:58.45,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k226}那个人已经来过了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.07,0:06:00.92,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k186}在我们抵达这里之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.17,0:06:04.44,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这个血染的杀人现场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.89,0:06:07.76,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}可是 池波女士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.59,0:06:13.91,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k270}柴田先生死去的时候右手中紧握着你的照片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.76,0:06:18.08,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}至少先对你们两个人的关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.19,0:06:22.94,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}以及那照片为何会在柴田先生手上等问题说明一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.38,0:06:26.28,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这些我全部都已经告诉过毛利先生了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.24,0:06:30.39,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那么就请你到警局把事情经过告诉我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.37,0:06:33.27,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我看这样好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.24,0:06:38.89,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k287}我到底该不该跟你们去警局 就让毛利小五郎先生来决定好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.09,0:06:45.13,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}如果他认为我真的有嫌疑而应该去接受讯问
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.55,0:06:46.93,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那我就跟你们去警局
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.65,0:06:51.37,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你认为怎么样 毛利先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.75,0:06:52.47,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}这…这个嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.51,0:06:54.84,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k76}还是去接受讯问比较好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.84,0:06:59.34,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我想应该没有这个必要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.95,0:07:00.61,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}毛利先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.11,0:07:03.97,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}毛利先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.56,0:07:05.09,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k145}毛利先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.85,0:07:10.74,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.47,0:07:14.69,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}毛…毛利先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.45,0:07:16.68,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k198}池波女士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.87,0:07:20.91,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k143}依这种情况来看 你还是去接受讯问吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.49,0:07:23.19,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我就说嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.55,0:07:26.02,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k106}不过 不是以嫌疑人的身份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.87,0:07:31.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}而是为了帮我接下来要说明的事件真相做证明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.30,0:07:34.16,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}以证人的身份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.10,0:07:37.69,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k281}那么 她就不是犯人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.22,0:07:38.73,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.46,0:07:40.88,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k124}如果她是犯人的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.35,0:07:46.83,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k190}为了去拿回照片而跟我们一起再来到这里的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.96,0:07:50.96,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}在按门铃后都没人回应的那段时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.91,0:07:57.34,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}她应该就会以玄关的门没锁为理由 进这个屋子里来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.12,0:08:04.35,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}如果她曾经来过这里 杀死柴田先生后再逃逸的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.46,0:08:08.98,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}她应该知道玄关的门没有上锁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.18,0:08:12.94,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}而且能够取回照片的机会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.54,0:08:19.18,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k236}只有在尸体被发现后 警方赶到现场前这段短暂的时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.91,0:08:25.51,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那么 难道犯人是当时确定门开着的吉川先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.94,0:08:26.75,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是你吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.68,0:08:32.23,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k174}对了 第一个发现尸体的人也是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.04,0:08:35.81,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你是不是掉了什么东西怕被我们警方发现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.90,0:08:39.33,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k287}所以才返回现场来拿啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.92,0:08:41.38,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}怎…怎么会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.77,0:08:44.81,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k185}不 吉川先生不是犯人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.34,0:08:49.63,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}如果遇害的柴田先生平常就不把门上锁的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.72,0:08:53.34,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}要猜出门没上锁是非常容易的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.82,0:08:58.25,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}而且在推算的案发时间里 没有不在场证明的吉川先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.48,0:09:02.79,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}如果再重回现场的话是非常危险的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.50,0:09:07.33,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}要是有必须拿回的东西他应该早就来拿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.90,0:09:12.34,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不可能杀了人之后又过了大半天才来拿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.45,0:09:14.86,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}如果他打电话来的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.00,0:09:19.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k155}就知道这房子里除了尸体以外没有其他人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.39,0:09:26.12,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}而且 他为什么要特意把要离开的我们给叫住呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.36,0:09:28.28,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}如果我是犯人的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.83,0:09:30.91,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k148}我会等这些来访的人走了以后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.21,0:09:33.39,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k238}自己再偷偷进来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.40,0:09:36.97,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那…那么犯人难道是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.68,0:09:42.24,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}对 乍看之下有不在场证明的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.93,0:09:44.06,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}就是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.89,0:09:51.57,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那…那么犯人难道是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.37,0:09:56.84,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}对 乍看之下有不在场证明的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.55,0:10:00.61,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}就是你 柴田恭子太太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.18,0:10:03.69,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}什么 柴田太太是凶手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.84,0:10:06.93,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k266}柴田太太 难道是你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.37,0:10:10.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}可是毛利先生…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.78,0:10:15.44,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k242}柴田太太准备早餐后 不是在五点时离开这里了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.10,0:10:21.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那桌上为什么还放着一份早上六点才送来的早报呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.21,0:10:27.65,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}而且 她朋友送她回来时已经是晚上七点多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.59,0:10:32.02,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}毛利先生当时你也在场啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.90,0:10:35.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你进来之后 她才刚回到家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.14,0:10:38.46,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那要怎么放那份早报呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.23,0:10:42.85,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}的确我到这里来的时候已经七点多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.27,0:10:46.47,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}事实上 你不觉得这是一种很模糊的表达方式吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.68,0:10:51.81,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}因为七点五分和七点十分都可以表达成七点多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.80,0:10:59.21,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}换句话说 柴田太太也有可能是在我们到达之前没多久回来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.59,0:11:01.12,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}等…等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.56,0:11:05.35,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k297}这么说的话 那个早餐难道是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.73,0:11:11.36,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}可能是她准备给凌晨三点左右回来的丈夫吃的夜宵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.17,0:11:15.89,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}但是 如果事后再摆上一份早报的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.14,0:11:18.77,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}就变成一顿完美的早餐了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.30,0:11:21.16,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}可是那个录影带呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.36,0:11:24.82,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k206}早上八点的古装剧录了以后就没拿出来不是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.38,0:11:27.41,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那很简单
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.91,0:11:33.42,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k153}只要事先把预约录影的时间延长 直到录影带录完就可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.46,0:11:37.03,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}换句话说这就是柴田太太的计谋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.11,0:11:43.16,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}首先她叫凌晨三点左右回来的丈夫去洗澡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.75,0:11:45.81,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}之后再让他消磨一些时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.64,0:11:48.35,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k289}然后在五点前以吃夜宵为由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.65,0:11:50.71,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}端出桌上那些饭菜给他吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.83,0:11:54.91,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}接下来 她叫正在吃夜宵的丈夫到走廊上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.08,0:11:58.68,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}然后用木刀从背后砍死他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.50,0:12:01.99,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}之后 准备好录影带
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.78,0:12:05.19,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}锁上玄关的门 然后离开家里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.06,0:12:11.38,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}在五点时到大楼下乘坐前来接她的朋友的车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.51,0:12:15.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}接下来 她只要在七点多之后回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.61,0:12:22.47,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}把信箱里的早报拿出来放在餐桌上 再报警的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.56,0:12:27.34,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不在场证明就完成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.78,0:12:28.78,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.17,0:12:33.51,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k139}这么一来即使之后让法医解剖尸体 都会让人认为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.03,0:12:36.65,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}她丈夫是早上八点左右在餐桌上吃早餐时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.20,0:12:39.19,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}被某个前来造访的人给杀害的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.49,0:12:44.41,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}可是柴田太太回来时 却发生了意想不到的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.08,0:12:47.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}原来应该倒在走廊上的柴田先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.64,0:12:52.51,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k257}因为想打电话求救 所以爬到客厅去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.68,0:12:53.77,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}对不对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.24,0:12:54.73,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k157}对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.57,0:12:58.92,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k132}柴田太太看到这种情形而惊慌失措
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.67,0:13:01.33,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}又听到电话铃声响起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.09,0:13:04.11,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k242}那通电话难道是我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.62,0:13:05.03,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k253}没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.70,0:13:09.07,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k108}就是吉川先生留在答录机里“我马上去找你”的那通电话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.27,0:13:13.46,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}柴田太太听到留言之后就开始想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.63,0:13:18.23,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}既然早报已经放在餐桌上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.52,0:13:20.68,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}与其现在报警
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.86,0:13:24.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}还不如让别人发现尸体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.61,0:13:26.95,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k275}然后自己再进门来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.17,0:13:30.17,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k256}这样比较不会让人怀疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.77,0:13:32.88,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那这段期间柴田太太躲在哪里呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.55,0:13:39.48,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k278}大概是躲在玄关旁边的逃生楼梯门后吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.08,0:13:41.51,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}直到吉川先生过来前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.08,0:13:47.28,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k199}不过 我们好像比吉川先生还早到一步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.83,0:13:51.21,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}可是侦探先生 那张照片是怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.88,0:13:54.92,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}为什么柴田先生手里握着那个人的照片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.44,0:13:58.35,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那是柴田太太为了伪装而混淆视听
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.67,0:14:01.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}故意让她先生握着的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.07,0:14:02.95,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}伪装
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.06,0:14:06.69,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k199}请先看看柴田先生的左手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.74,0:14:10.11,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}他的手心沾满血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.21,0:14:13.19,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k247}可是无名指上缠着的绷带却没有任何血迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.50,0:14:17.75,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}的…的确
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.16,0:14:20.25,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k166}接下来是右手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.03,0:14:24.13,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这…这是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.13,0:14:26.85,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}难道这是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.29,0:14:27.84,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k216}没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.94,0:14:31.15,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k165}在柴田太太来到客厅之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.47,0:14:34.01,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k252}柴田先生已经握在手里了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.72,0:14:37.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那就是他们夫妇的证明 结婚戒指
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.25,0:14:46.48,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}柴田太太发现她丈夫左手无名指上的结婚戒指不见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.11,0:14:50.94,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}后来她立刻注意到戒指是握在她丈夫的右手里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.57,0:14:55.42,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}所以她就把他僵硬的右手给扳开 将戒指拿了出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.48,0:15:01.27,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}可是这么一来 右手会很明显让人觉得不自然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.85,0:15:08.59,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}所以她才会想到 让他握着那张夹在书里的池波女士的照片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.91,0:15:11.65,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.23,0:15:16.31,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k132}只要不把目标指向自己 任何东西都无所谓了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.84,0:15:17.36,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.87,0:15:22.86,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k103}然后她想把戒指戴回他左手的无名指上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.38,0:15:26.07,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}可是却发现手指弯曲戴不进去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.95,0:15:28.99,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}所以 她才在左手无名指上缠上绷带
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.26,0:15:31.25,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k231}想要借此来隐藏戒指的痕迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.08,0:15:37.46,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}至于小指上也缠上绷带 可能是为了不让无名指看起来太过醒目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.51,0:15:41.98,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}横沟警官 绷带下面真的有戒指的痕迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.90,0:15:44.43,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}马上拍照存证
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.99,0:15:46.53,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k208}好 接下来是找戒指
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.85,0:15:48.68,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k186}屋里各个角落请务必彻底搜查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.95,0:15:51.36,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}不用了 应该没有这个必要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.88,0:15:56.84,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我想东西应该还在柴田太太身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.64,0:16:02.32,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}即使把血迹擦掉之后还是会有鲁米诺反应的戒指
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.09,0:16:06.94,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}在警方马上赶到的情况下她没把握能够把它藏好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.97,0:16:09.79,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}当然曾经藏身的逃生楼梯也不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.72,0:16:15.83,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k274}最安全的方法 应该是等警察回去之后再处理掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.90,0:16:19.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}所以证物应该还在柴田太太身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.62,0:16:23.61,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}柴田先生死前紧握着的结婚戒指
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.03,0:16:26.89,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}就是表示她是犯人的死亡讯息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.77,0:16:40.04,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}果然还是不能做坏事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.32,0:16:45.47,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}可是为什么我丈夫跟吉川先生 做的坏事却不会曝光呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.81,0:16:48.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你们不觉得不公平吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.41,0:16:50.59,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k260}是麻将
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.39,0:16:54.73,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k197}我丈夫他们天天都沉迷与麻将桌上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.40,0:16:58.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}而且他们赌的金额很大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.10,0:16:59.78,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}拜他们所赐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.04,0:17:03.62,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k94}电脑 珠宝 汽车 LD 音箱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.20,0:17:05.83,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}一个接一个被卖掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.40,0:17:08.62,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}都是拜这所赐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.81,0:17:14.33,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我丈夫说下一个要卖的是我的高尔夫球具
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.88,0:17:16.08,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}而且他还说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.36,0:17:20.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k148}下一次要卖我们结婚时我爸送给他的礼物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.59,0:17:22.97,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}请跟我们到警局走一趟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.33,0:17:24.24,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k274}好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.91,0:17:27.54,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k258}我换件衣服马上来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.21,0:17:34.29,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}礼物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.31,0:17:36.26,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k209}是刀吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.37,0:17:37.42,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k107}难…难道是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.88,0:17:42.95,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不要过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.63,0:17:47.01,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我真的别无选择
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.81,0:17:50.46,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k218}我只有这样做才能阻止我丈夫的恶行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.66,0:17:51.45,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k185}柴田太太 冷静一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.40,0:17:56.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k274}已经没用了 因为我杀了人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.40,0:17:57.27,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}柴田太太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.57,0:17:58.85,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k118}请你退后一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.10,0:18:11.24,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你要做什么 不要过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.00,0:18:15.89,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我不是叫你不要过来吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.12,0:18:24.22,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}混蛋 你还想杀人吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.26,0:18:32.07,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你杀了你丈夫之后还想继续杀人吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.82,0:18:33.84,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}杀…杀人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.81,0:18:36.23,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k199}我只是想自杀而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.33,0:18:37.02,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k152}笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.29,0:18:39.17,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k96}人的生命是没有你我之分的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.48,0:18:41.24,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k219}绝对不能轻易地夺走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.82,0:18:44.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k234}只要是夺走生命的笨蛋都是杀人凶手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.92,0:18:48.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}即使是夺走自己的生命也一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.61,0:18:50.61,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k269}你好好记住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.53,0:18:56.86,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我们走吧 警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.18,0:18:58.99,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k265}啊 是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.63,0:19:02.68,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}在这之前 池波女士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.78,0:19:06.01,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你是不是应该说明一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.01,0:19:09.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你说的四个谎言到底是什么意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.20,0:19:14.31,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你的支气管不好却喜欢织毛衣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.43,0:19:16.65,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这一点实在令人难以理解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.37,0:19:20.29,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k294}只看到鱼片就知道鱼的种类
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.77,0:19:22.87,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这证明你很擅长做菜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.07,0:19:25.34,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}而且你已经结婚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.46,0:19:29.51,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k239}你左手无名指上遮住的戒指痕迹显示了这一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.49,0:19:31.97,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}再就是レイコ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.71,0:19:37.05,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k222}那本忍者小说里并没有人叫这个名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.27,0:19:44.21,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你在咖啡店里说的レイコ到底是什么意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.37,0:19:47.72,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不是レイコ 是冷咖…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.18,0:19:52.09,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}大阪人称冰咖啡为冷咖啡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.86,0:19:54.83,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}她本来想点冰咖啡说到一半停了下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.20,0:19:57.68,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k234}是害怕自己是大阪人的身份会曝光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.71,0:20:02.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}现在会这么说的只有大叔大婶这辈人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.44,0:20:06.48,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是不是啊 大婶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.42,0:20:09.05,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k298}服部跟和叶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.64,0:20:10.45,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k223}不会吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.33,0:20:13.55,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k268}喂 大婶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.71,0:20:14.88,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k138}你的工作不是已经结束了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.05,0:20:16.34,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k134}快回大阪去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.28,0:20:19.26,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k223}喂 你这样子大婶大婶的叫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.37,0:20:21.29,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k209}对静华女士太没礼貌了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.08,0:20:23.51,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k271}我怎么叫她都无所谓吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.77,0:20:25.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k169}因为她是我妈呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.63,0:20:32.21,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}骗人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.31,0:20:34.99,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k168}她的肤色没有你那么黑啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.33,0:20:37.98,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}说这个太失礼了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.27,0:20:40.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k194}我的肤色是遗传我爷爷的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.61,0:20:42.14,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k234}怎么会这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.53,0:20:54.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}虽然未来 不全都是美好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.99,0:21:09.72,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}可以确定的是现在 正迈向未来 比任何人更耀眼地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.67,0:21:26.32,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}站在这里 即使是为了 即将粉碎的现实而流泪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.65,0:21:32.53,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}We can start in my life 一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.78,0:21:36.87,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}伴随着永不放弃的梦想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.79,0:21:48.92,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}喂 就因为可以遇见 另一个自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.42,0:21:56.34,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}才能将心情 转变成唯一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.35,0:22:01.98,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}看 让我们就从这里开始吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.69,0:22:07.36,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}Just start in my life
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.73,0:22:10.98,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}什么 你是来试探的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.15,0:22:12.12,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k242}试探我吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.43,0:22:13.78,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k128}对 没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.37,0:22:18.99,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k193}平次每次跟毛利侦探在一起的时候都会受伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.27,0:22:19.97,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我以为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.09,0:22:22.66,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k82}毛利先生为了让他多学习一点侦探知识
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:22.79,0:22:25.77,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k270}就让他做一些过于艰难的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.40,0:22:32.13,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}而且上次你到大阪的时候也没来我家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.53,0:22:37.78,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}所以我不放心 以为你是个没血没泪不通情理的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:38.14,0:22:40.03,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}什么嘛 上次我受伤住院的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:40.43,0:22:43.07,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k229}你还不是一样没来医院看我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.62,0:22:45.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我越想越不放心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:45.46,0:22:48.36,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k184}所以决定来看看你到底是个什么样的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:48.49,0:22:51.37,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}见过你之后 我才知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.52,0:22:53.12,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}毛利先生会被平次钦佩是因为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:53.28,0:22:56.56,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k176}你人好 头脑又聪明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:56.87,0:22:58.35,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}谢谢你的夸奖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:58.63,0:23:01.84,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k177}我跟四朗先生以电话商量好的寻人事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:01.92,0:23:03.81,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}以及我撒的谎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:03.92,0:23:06.36,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}还有意外碰到的杀人事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:06.48,0:23:09.78,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k256}你竟然能在这么短的时间之内解决
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.30,0:23:12.82,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}虽然四朗先生遭遇不幸让我很难过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:13.56,0:23:16.54,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不过找了很久的照片终于回到我身边了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.12,0:23:18.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}亏你还说得出口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:19.03,0:23:19.93,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k191}这张照片是你输给一个一年级的女生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:20.02,0:23:21.52,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k99}哭得很伤心的时候拍的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.73,0:23:24.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k171}所以你不是说不想把它拿回来吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.02,0:23:28.55,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这样子我就可以放心地把平次跟和叶交给你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:29.49,0:23:30.33,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}交给我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:31.03,0:23:33.96,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k154}对了 他们两个人为什么拿着行李
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:34.82,0:23:36.99,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}咦 你们没听这个小鬼告诉你们吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:39.92,0:23:42.66,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}咦 那通电话是认真的吗
